A bug affecting file descriptor callbacks and timers crept in in the
recent release of the CamlTk interface for Caml Light (the Objective Caml
version is not affected).
A patch for camltk.c is now available by anonymous FTP
ftp://ftp.inria.fr/INRIA/Projects/cristal/caml-light/camltk/cl-patch1

